OL,3,CMan in a critical condition after a
OL,4,Csuspected homophobic attack in Bristol
OL,6,FA man is in a critical condition after
OL,7,Fa suspected homophobic attack in
OL,8,FBristol city centre.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to St
OL,11,FNicholas Street in the early hours of
OL,12,FFriday, April 24 after a man in his
OL,13,F30s was found lying unconscious with
OL,14,Fsignificant facial injuries.
OL,16,FHe was taken to hospital, but his
OL,17,Fhealth has deteriorated and he is now
OL,18,Fin a critical but stable condition.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
