CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1777641071
OL,3,CMan in a critical condition after a
OL,4,Csuspected homophobic attack in Bristol
OL,6,FAnother man sustained minor injuries
OL,7,Fin the incident, which police are
OL,8,Ftreating as a hate crime.
OL,10,FA spokesman for Avon and Somerset
OL,11,FPolice said: "We are concerned that
OL,12,Fthe incident may include a homophobic
OL,13,Fhate crime element.
OL,15,F"An initial account was provided by a
OL,16,Fsecond victim who had sustained minor
OL,17,Finjuries in the same incident, which
OL,18,Fdid not require hospital treatment.
OL,26,@sD@NOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1777641071
OL,3,CMan in a critical condition after a
OL,4,Csuspected homophobic attack in Bristol
OL,6,F"He has since been able to provide
OL,7,Fmore information, which means we are
OL,8,Finvestigating the possibility that
OL,9,Fthere could have potentially been a
OL,10,Fhomophobic motivation to what took
OL,11,Fplace."
OL,13,FNeighbourhood Chief Inspector Keith
OL,14,FSmith said: "We are treating this
OL,15,Fincident seriously and have briefed
OL,16,Flocal LGBTQ+ leaders and SARI (Stand
OL,17,FAgainst Racism & Inequality) of the
OL,18,Fcurrent situation, because we have
OL,19,Frecorded this as a hate crime.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@GO]vD@MOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1777641071
OL,3,CMan in a critical condition after a
OL,4,Csuspected homophobic attack in Bristol
OL,6,F"Detectives are seeking to gain a full
OL,7,Funderstanding of what happened, which
OL,8,Fis why we are appealing for anyone
OL,9,Fwith information to come forward.
OL,11,F"At this stage there is no evidence to
OL,12,Fsuggest a wider risk to the public,
OL,13,Fbut we wish to identify the offenders
OL,14,Fas soon as possible.
OL,16,F"We believe the assaults were carried
OL,17,Fout by a group of three or four men
OL,18,Fand they are thought to have made off
OL,19,Fon foot initially and then driven away
OL,20,Fin a car.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
