PN,43205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1777641071
OL,3,CMan in a critical condition after a
OL,4,Csuspected homophobic attack in Bristol
OL,6,F"One man is believed to have been
OL,7,Fwearing a blue jacket, with two others
OL,8,Fdressed predominantly in black or grey.
OL,10,FAnyone with information can contact
OL,11,Fpolice on 101 and quote reference
OL,12,F5226111583.
OL,14,FAlternatively, Crimestoppers can be
OL,15,Fcontacted anonymously on 0800 555111
OL,16,For via its website.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
